---
import { DownloadSimple } from "@phosphor-icons/react";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="简历｜庞成康">
  <div class="page-shell resume-page">
    <header class="page-header resume-heading">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Resume</p>
        <h1>简历</h1>
        <p>这里保留公开的教育、工作与项目经历。</p>
      </div>
      <button class="secondary-button" type="button" onclick="window.print()">
        <DownloadSimple size={18} /> 打印或保存 PDF
      </button>
    </header>

    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>个人简介</h2>
      <p>关注内容组织、产品体验与前端实现，擅长把复杂问题拆解成可执行的步骤。</p>
    </section>
    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>能力方向</h2>
      <div class="resume-skills">
        <span>内容架构</span><span>前端开发</span><span>数据可视化</span>
        <span>项目复盘</span><span>知识管理</span><span>持续学习</span>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="resume-section">
      <h2>项目经历</h2>
      <div class="resume-item">
        <div><strong>个人知识主页</strong><time>2026 — 至今</time></div>
        <p>完成需求梳理、视觉设计、内容建模与前端实现，建立长期可维护的个人内容系统。</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
